overview: Ellie Cachette is a technical project manager and entrepreneur with a background in payment solutions and technologies. Ellie founded ConsumerBell to help consumers collaborate their complaints against corporations for faster resolution. Ellie is also an avid sailor and a strong supporter of Women2.0, a Silicon Valley organization dedicated to empowering female entrepreneurs.
